Set Shell zsh

Output loop.gif

Set FontSize 15
Set Width 600
Set Height 400
Set Padding 15
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set Theme "nord"
Require lpx

Hide

Type@10ms lpx earth.gif
Enter
Sleep 1s

Show

Sleep 500ms

Type@300ms "LL"
Sleep 300ms

Type "["
Sleep 500ms

Type@300ms "Llll"

Type "]"
Sleep 500ms

Type@300ms "hhh"
Sleep 300ms

Space
Sleep 4s
Space

Sleep 500ms
